# Cloudflare Pages SPA fall-through.
#
# Every unmatched path is rewritten (status 200, not a 30x redirect) so
# React Router and Clerk's path-based sub-routes (/sign-in/sso-callback,
# /sign-in/factor-two, ...) work after a hard refresh or direct link.
#
# Note: this rewrites to `/`, not `/index.html`.  Cloudflare's modern
# Workers-based Pages deploys reject `/* /index.html 200` as a false-
# positive "infinite loop" (https://github.com/cloudflare/workers-sdk/issues/11824)
# even though that rule is universally correct.  Rewriting to `/` and
# letting Cloudflare's default html_handling serve `index.html` from
# there is functionally identical and passes the deploy validator.
/*    /    200
